description.plain:
Elliott Platt, better known as ElyOtto, is a 17-year-old artist from Calgary, Canada. His music is a blend of EDM, Hyperpop and Folk-Punk.

His first upload on Soundcloud was an EDM remix of SpectralouS’s “Visions”, published March 31, 2018.

ElyOtto has released three singles to date: “Let Go :(,” and “SugarCrash!.”

“SugarCrash!” is by far the most popular of the three, thanks to its ubiquitous presence in the background of TikTok videos. The track has been streamed over 110 million times on Spotify.

songs.title: SugarCrash!

description.plain:
An early-2000s internet-inspired hyperpop song, “SugarCrash!” is a single by ElyOtto which takes elements from pitched-up and nightcore sounds, as well as hyperpop and electronic autotune, with evil metaphors to create a “so unique, it’s good” nostalgic feel.

The song went on to gain more popularity and success when it started trending on TikTok.
